"[cultist]: -8. Draw a card or gain a resource.\n"
"[tablet]: -4. If you fail and it is your turn, lose all remaining actions and end your turn.\n"
"[elder_thing]: -5. If you fail, take 1 damage and 1 horror."
msgstr ""
